trailingComments.value:
*
 * Convert milliseconds to hours and minutes
 *
 * @param {number} milliseconds Milliseconds
 * @returns {{minutes: number, hours: number}} Time object
 *
 * @example
 * parseMillisecondsToTime(((1 * 60) + 15) * 60 * 1000);
 * //=> {hours: 1, minutes: 15}
